data.description: Beautiful Low-County Style home in sought after Riverlights Community. Don't wait to build, this like new home is available now for a quick close. This charmiing home greets you and your guests with a covered patio and spacious upstairs covered deck. Inside the home you will appreciate tons of windows and natural light. Wide plank LVP flooring throughout both floors with ceramic tile in the bathrooms. First floor has a wonderful open floorplan with a dining area providing separation from the kitchen to living room. The kitchen features a massive island with quartz counters, offering a great prep space for the family chef. Gas stove, tile backspalsh and beautiful soft close cabinets. A walk in pantry and half both complete the downstairs. Upstairs master suite features a walk in tiled shower and double vanity. Two additional BR's share another full bath upstairs. Guest BR provides access to top floor porch. Sellers added a deck in the backyard which leads to a detached 2 car garage. Riverlights has miles of paved paths circling large ponds with fountains. Community, pool, fitness center and convenient access to restaurants and shopping make this a very desirable location!
